{"tid":377283,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[人口統計] 搭巴士坐上層,要落車時,會唔會喺架車郁緊嗰陣行樓梯?","createTime":"2017-08-27T15:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T16:54:50.000Z","uid":87511,"like":59,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21dd63aba1bb7130f1047081b89eb4255aee7828","tid":377283,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:26:31.000Z","msg":"正評-會<br />\n會,因為唔想阻住其他人<br />\n個個都埋站先行落車咪搞到大塞車?<br />\n洗唔洗幫你鋪埋紅地氈?<br />\n<br />\n負評-唔會<br />\n唔會,因為唔想整親自己<br />\n真係咁唔好彩整到行唔到,要call白車<br />\n到時成車人+成條馬路嘅人多得你唔少 <br />\n<br />\n利申 畀咗負評自己"},{"pid":"93672a4fed55dcbdd3761003e0f744edb78bd83c","tid":377283,"uid":13288,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:28:16.000Z","msg":"紅綠燈位停車落去是常識吧"},{"pid":"5ae1369859836fd31291a133703ad6b73963de33","tid":377283,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:28:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>紅綠燈位停車落去是常識吧</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個情況當係負評<br />\n<br />\n因為我都會咁做"},{"pid":"383921ac2f1c56dc76a86901f09f1b4e2ea51f0f","tid":377283,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:30:07.000Z","msg":"如果冇其他人落車<br />\n停站先行落去好似阻住全車人咁<br />\n有啲唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf59779ff787e8e44e392ff92bb05dd503a7c35","tid":377283,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:32:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果冇其他人落車<br />\n停站先行落去好似阻住全車人咁<br />\n有啲唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中學嗰陣<br />\n聽過隔離班有個同學仔返學嗰陣搭巴士<br />\n巴士郁緊嗰陣喺上層行行下仆親,要打999搵救護車<br />\n仲要成兩個星期冇返學<br />\n<br />\n自始之後我就變咗腐皮嗰種人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n勿相認 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fce417027192ce56bf8ed03676a0a9f7cd0941b","tid":377283,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:37:10.000Z","msg":"最主要係驚我落到去已經關左門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03bbeeb8125e0ef84f083a8da7f6308c9570324a","tid":377283,"uid":37153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:50:07.000Z","msg":"唔敢 細個試過以為佢停車 點知落落下一開仆左落去"},{"pid":"3fccaa662c7660eec6ca0fada78523f7c91a472a","tid":377283,"uid":35504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:52:21.000Z","msg":"停燈或者大直路落+緊握扶手"},{"pid":"59f3a20f97a078776de186bce4781a1ae4806417","tid":377283,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:54:16.000Z","msg":"睇落車個站而定<br />\n有啲站知道係多人落車，又唔趕時間嘅，咪慢慢落<br />\n如果要喺啲第一次去嘅站落，又或者知道冇乜人落<br />\n就會上個站閂門後就開始行落去"},{"pid":"9a55bd48299b912634866f759dd789eb75982864","tid":377283,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:56:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果冇其他人落車<br />\n停站先行落去好似阻住全車人咁<br />\n有啲唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中學嗰陣<br />\n聽過隔離班有個同學仔返學嗰陣搭巴士<br />\n巴士郁緊嗰陣喺上層行行下仆親,要打999搵救護車<br />\n仲要成兩個星期冇返學<br />\n<br />\n自始之後我就變咗腐皮嗰種人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n勿相認 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你呢個情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我住鄉村 啲巴士一定西到癡線<br />\n有日見到個附近鄰居已經包晒嘢單腳棟住兩枝叉行 佢重可以上樓上 仲要喺架車係咁郁未停定嘅時候就行落車<br />\n我睇到眼都凸埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab23b4b114df396b669043156ec4475d53f9cf4","tid":377283,"uid":53037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T16:02:50.000Z","msg":"正常情況都係會係架車停紅綠燈時落定去先<br />\n但搵唔到機會時會企定係上層等到停車時即刻落去<br />\n有次試過後面果種情況因為架車開得好快又無紅燈落唔到去<br />\n一停即落下層但落到去個巴士佬係我面前關咗門<br />\n即刻嗌有落點知個司機屌返我<br />\n然後我落咗車即刻記低佢車牌投訴佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"014d4a2def276d41a094ed3bda45d981d9d5fcca","tid":377283,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T16:49:48.000Z","msg":"要行樓梯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4808dcb2a4f5b40b612285c5a8c6646f193ca794","tid":377283,"uid":71824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T16:54:50.000Z","msg":"正評<br />\n<br />\n唔識扶住落?"}]}